監理所嘉雲區車輛行車事故鑑定會\r\n      鑑定意見書（嘉雲區0000000案）1份。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDM/111%2c%e5%98%89%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c319%2c20220412%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,111,嘉交簡,319,20220412,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"嘉交簡","JNO":"319","JDATE":"20220412","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}